        <h2>To put it simply</h2>
        <p class="lead">
          This entire project is to help men and really anyone to improve their
          lives. While many of the writings in this blog are focused on male
          improvement from a male prospective, many, and really most the lessons
          can easily translate to females and non-binary as well. As we are all
          quite similar in the end with the exception of our glaring
          differences.
        </p>
