        <p class="lead">To explain in greater detail...</p>
        <p>
          There is a massive need in the United States and the world in general
          to teach our young people how to succeed, and more often than not the
          twelve years of schooling that students receive is missing a massive
          amount of knowledge that we as people need to succeed. With the
          current times where so may children are growing up without quality
          mentors and role models, the hope is to create a resource of knowledge
          that people can look to that will guid them in the places of their
          lives where they're uncertain.
        </p>
