          goal is to teach, train and lead our younger people and especially our
          young boys to fit into a future that is often confusing to know how to
          act. While simple advice like just be nice to everyone and don't judge
          other people unless you have walked in their shoes should suffice; in
          all reality it lacks the specifics that people need to know to be
          successful in life.
        </p>
